entries.femaleVariant: Heywood's a rough neighborhood.
Can I ask a personal question?
Heywood's a rough place for biz, huh? Gotta be rough, keeping it all in check.
Why'd you become a priest?
You ever visit Mama Welles?
Need info on Dex.
Listen... You ever check up on Mama Welles? Might need someone, now that Jackie's gone.
Sure. But I may not answer.
Why'd you join the priesthood?
Faith is God's grace. For many years, I did not feel it. But eventually, that changed.
I believe in God, V. And I only hope that when I pass, He believes in me.
Padre, I need some advice. From an old friend.
She's a strong woman. She'd do just fine without me.
You know what I mean. Jackie had his secrets. Someone might wanna get even.
Nobody'll touch her. Trust me.
And besides – you should also stop by and see her. It's only right.
That's the thing with old friends. They never refuse.
Dexter DeShawn. You heard anything about him?
Besides what everyone else has?
Tell you this – Dex will not get past the pearly gates. Unless he buys off St. Peter.
Not really. All you can get here is enough respect to keep the wolves from eating you alive.
This is your turf. Must have something under control.
Just got the most wolves afraid of me.
We'll talk later.
Talk later.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Vaya con Dios." t="Go with God." b="" a=""/>
Heard you're home.
Heard there's a new soul in Heywood. I am Sebastian Ibarra. They call me Padre.
Already? Sure got that ear to the ground.
Always. Anyway, you need something – you know where to find me.
V. Nice to meet you.
I like people who understand the value of respect. We'll be in touch, V.
